Text:
"Not even remotely pretty"

What colour's the sky in your world?

Someone said Eva Green is ugly? Lol. Too bad the comment must have been deleted.

I'm the sort of man who idolizes no one. But you know, and I actually have put thought into this, I can't think of any other famous actress/model(or women I haven't met in general) I'd really pray to have a shot with if we ever came to share some kind of routine.
